column5: Happy birthday!  Mike

Joe...... Hope today was just the greatest bud! You didnt ask Art for a car did you? .So what is this........it's your 32nd is'nt it? btw..them jeans just keep on ticking...I think I wear them every day I go to work and theres no sign of stress on them anywhere.must be some sort of 'Southern' type of denim..... Hope to see you an Art at Lakair.we're trying are dangest to get there. Play safe but have a blast Joe. -peter
Oh ya, I forgot about the Jeans, ha ha ha.  That was funny  Joey
Hope you are having a great day Joe! Happy Birthday!
Enjoy your day!  Bly
Coonasses don't get old, they just smell that way  :lol:  :lol:  :lol:  :lol: JUST KIDDING, have a great day Joe!!
Have a good one.
Joe you have to spend more time in Canada as Canadians age slower than Americans....something about the beer!
HAPPY BIRTHDAY, hope it has been a good one for ya and many more to come!  jason
Hope you had a great day Joe! Happy Birthday bud.   Whopper
Sorry I'm late, but Happy Birthday Joe!!!
Happy Bday bud!!
Well, as usual; I'm a day late and a dollar short!  Just remember; getting older is good!  Happy birthday!
Why is it I only hear people over 45 say this????   Art
Happy Birthday Joe, hope you enjoyed the day.  Mike
Happy Birthday!!
I hope you scheduled the day lite so you can have some fun on your Birthday.   Art
Happy Birthday there Joe! Do y'all sing Happy Birthday in Cajun? Have a great day, Bubba.
Hey Joe, Happy B-Day my friend, and all the best to ya !  Good to see I'm not the only one gettin older !!
All the "BEST"of this day to you Joe and many many more to ya.......
Nah Roy, they shoot eachother with Paintballs    , so Joe, don't forget to duck  And have a great day  Maureen
Joe,  Happy birthday brother!  Gerritt.
Have a great day and happy birthday
Happy Birthday Joe,and have yourself a great day.You wanna be COONASS  Steve
Happy birthday!! Hope you have a great day!
Happy Birfday,  Joe, Best Fishes too.
Happy birthday kid!
have a great day
Happy Birthday Joe and have a great day.  Best regards, Sam
Thanx Guys...I'm sure it'll be a good day. Joe
Happy birthday Joe!!
Happy Birthday! Hope you have a great day and find some time to make loud noises!
Happy Birthday Joe     Hope you have a wonderful day and that no good brother of yours gets you something  Joey
Dang!  I'm going to have to check who's logged in once in awhile around here.  I keep upping Tybo's post count  Joey
